      {
        "start": "04:10.900",
        "end": "04:14.500",
        "original": "「ウタ」を知ってから、数日が経った。",
        "english": "A few days have passed since I learned about 'songs'.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:15.500",
        "end": "04:21.500",
        "original": "旅路は進み、ようやく光の塔がおぼろげながらに見えてくる",
        "english": "My journey continues, and at last, the Tower of Light is coming into view, however faintly.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:22.300",
        "end": "04:28.500",
        "original": "だけど「オンガク」や「ウタ」について知っている人は、ほとんどいなかった",
        "english": "But there were almost no people who knew about 'music' or 'songs'.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:29.300",
        "end": "04:35.100",
        "original": "もしかしたらあたしは、ないものねだりをしているだけなのかもしれない",
        "english": "Maybe I'm just asking for the impossible.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:36.100",
        "end": "04:39.500",
        "original": "でも……新しい出会いはあった",
        "english": "But... there was a new encounter.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:41.700",
        "end": "04:45.300",
        "original": "Ciaooo! I'm Raora Panthera!",
        "english": "Ciaooo! I'm Raora Panthera!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:46.000",
        "end": "04:49.000",
        "original": "あたし、絵描きをやってるんだ！",
        "english": "I'm an artist!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:49.500",
        "end": "04:55.300",
        "original": "きみをみたとき、ビビッてきたの！きみにはこれが似合いそう！",
        "english": "When I saw you, I felt a spark! This would look good on you!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:56.500",
